reviews: Solid construction and massive value for money. The Headphone hanger is made with aluminium so is light and easy to install. There is padding on the clasp mechanism for attaching to your furniture so you pick that nice desktop or cabinet without worrying about metal grinding it's way in or you having to slot some paper/cardboard in to reduce damage. The hanger folds up and clicks satisfyingly into place. Once deployed the arm can easily accommodate your headphones with two slots added to the base of the arm to manage your cords. Great little unit at a great price. I cannot recommend enough if you are seeking a similar solution.
